data.eml:eml: The types of Phasmida in the Natural History Museum, London, UK

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Brock, Paul D., Marshall, Judith A., Beccaloni, George W., Harman, Allan J. E. (2016): The types of Phasmida in the Natural History Museum, London, UK. Zootaxa 4179 (2): 151-208, DOI: http://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4179.2.1
